Definition: a process for identifying minerals or crystals
Example: a small rod is coated with a powdered form of the substance and subjected to suitably modified X-rays; the pattern of diffracted rings is used for identification
Synonyms: powder_method, powder_technique, photography, a, process, for, identifying, minerals, or, crystals, small, rod, is, coated, with, powdered, form, of, the, substance, and, subjected, to, suitably, modified, X-rays, pattern, diffracted, rings, used, identification
Category: noun.process
